header.name: LG's Cute Mash Up [v1.17.2]
header.description: Compiled by LadyGodiva222. A collection of original and modified addons. Includes: Sakura Trees by LadyGodiva222, Blushing Ghast by Haisuki, Kawaii World! Paintings by mariiecx, So Kawaii! by snowybunny, a selection of armors from maid armor! by splder, and Kal's Dye Pots, a modified Light Armor collection, and turle helmet from Kal's Heavy Armor Addon [Bedrock] by Kalam0n. See readme.txt for more details.
